# CoreOps bot factory output (Termux runtime artifact — not source)
# This directory is LITERALLY named "${HOME}" (the characters $, {, H, O, M, E, })
# due to an unexpanded shell variable in a bot script. gitignore does not expand
# variables, so this pattern matches the literal directory name.
${HOME}/

